His spells are crap you say?  I'm going to just ask you this: &quot;Could you -make- any better?&quot;.  Go ahead and say &quot;they won't let me near the source code&quot;..  Because if you want to get technical, then I guess Al`Kabor didn't even make the spells, now did he?  They were created by a Verant programmer.  I think you can see my point..<br>
<br>
Stop flaming the poor guy, if you wanna flame someone, flame Verant programmers or some other poor fellow who is just trying to help you guys while you crap on him (Poe).<br>
